performance. For the sake of completeness, we also investigate the recognition performance gains that we can obtain by employing
classification ensembles. A ranking system based upon recognition and computational performance is proposed. MCRGNet, Radio Galaxy Zoo and ConvXpress (novel classifier) are the architectures that best balance computational requirements with recognition performance.},
