each SNIa survey strategy. A strategy optimized for high-redshift SNIa
discovery is preferred when considering the constraints possible from
both SNIa and lensed SN cosmology, also delivering {\textasciitilde}1.5 times more
lensed SN than other proposed survey strategies.},
