	abstract = {We perform a semi-automated search for strong gravitational lensing systems in the 9,000 deg\${\textasciicircum}2\$ Dark Energy Camera Legacy Survey (DECaLS), part of the DESI Legacy Imaging Surveys (Dey et al.). The combination of the depth and breadth of these surveys are unparalleled at this time, making them particularly suitable for discovering new strong
